{"type": "article", "id": 24933, "title": "复古黄铜吊灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-05T07:03:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607104233q0ORwDCYZ9TIdWA6.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是纽约的设计工作室 Apparatu 展出的两款灯具，都采用了黄铜灯罩来体现古典。其中一款灯是椭圆形的，两两垂直错位形成一个较大的灯，有音阶的韵律。另一款灯是在黄铜灯罩下装上圆筒形的玻璃瓶，可以是单独的灯罩和玻璃瓶或者一个大灯罩下很多玻璃瓶，都像是垂下来的光束，拥有明暗变化和质感。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104231tBJbE9Ql1RMK4DrS.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.70415648\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071042315HY8qSAR6QjgJZuO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70415648\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104232wWfjvAs7aJLn3Gly.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70415648\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104232UvIHnEdig8zQuhJG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63447433\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}